condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Annual Work Plans, Section I(B) 1 of the Schedule to the Project Agreement | Description :Jiangxi prepares,submits a draft Annual Work Plan for Bank review by October 31 in each year, and ensures Project implementation in accordance withthe Annual Work Plans agreed with the Bank and in a manner satisfactory to the Bank. Amendments to the Annual Work Plans requireprior written agreement of the Bank. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Institutional Arrangements, Section I(A) of the Schedule to th Project Agreement | Description :Jiangximaintains a Provincial Steering Committee, a PPMO at the provincial level and a Project Leading Group, a PMO at each of its eightProject counties. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Mid-term review, Section II.2 of the Schedule to the Project Agreement | Description :Jiangxi furnishes to theBank a mid-term review report for the Project, summarizing the result of the monitoring and evaluation activities carried out fromthe inception of the Project, and setting out the measures recommended to ensure the efficient completion of the Project and theachievement of the objectives thereof during the period following such data. | Due Date :31-Aug-2020

Finance Agreement :Project Implementation Manual, Section I(B) 2 of the Schedule, Project Agreement | Description :Jiangxi appliesthe Project Implementation Manual throughout Project implementation in a timely and efficient manner satisfactory to the Bank.Amendments to the Project Implementation Manual require prior written agreement of the Bank. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Risk-sharing Transfers, Section I (F) of Schedule to the Project Agreement | Description :Jiangxi enters into aRisk Sharing Agreement with JACB, and Implementation Agreement with the eligible beneficiaries. Amendments to any Risk SharingAgreement or the Implementation Agreement require agreement of the Borrower and the Bank. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Safeguards, Section I (C) of the Schedule to the Project Agreement | Description :Jiangxi carries out Projectactivities in accordance with the provisions of the Safeguards Instruments. Amendments to any of these Safeguards Instrumentsrequire prior written agreement of the Bank. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Sub-grants, Section I (E) of Schedule to the Project Agreement | Description :Jiangxi provides sub-grants inaccordance with eligibility criteria and procedures acceptable to the Bank and under a Sub-grant Agreement on terms and conditionsapproved by the Bank. Amendments to any Sub-grant Agreement require agreement of the Borrower and the Bank. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS
